Class StringCollection

java.lang.Object
au.csiro.pathling.fhirpath.collection.Collection
au.csiro.pathling.fhirpath.collection.StringCollection
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable, Equatable, Materializable, Numeric, StringCoercible
public class StringCollection extends Collection implements Comparable, Numeric, StringCoercible, Materializable
Represents a FHIRPath expression which refers to a string typed element.
Author:
John Grimes
